    "class": "name"
   },
   "html": "\n[ なかじま・ちくへい ]"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "prof"
   },
   "html": "\n商工相、軍需相、鉄相、中島飛行機社長、中島派政友会総裁、商工政務次官、海軍大尉"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "table",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "lt"
   },
   "html": "<tbody><tr><td class=\"lt\"><a href=\"05n.html\">一覧　（ナ）</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href=\"http://www.amazon.co.jp/exec/obidos/redirect?link_code=ur2&amp;tag=click20thcetu-22&amp;camp=247&amp;creative=1211&amp;path=external-search%3Fsearch-type=ss%26index=books-jp%26keyword=%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25B3%25B6%2520%25E7%259F%25A5%25E4%25B9%2585%25E5%25B9%25B3\" target=\"_blank\">本を入手</a><img src=\"http://www.assoc-amazon.jp/e/ir?t=click20thcetu-22&amp;l=ur2&amp;o=9\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"border:none !important; margin:0px !important;\"></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td></tr></tbody>"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "off"
   },
   "html": "<span class=\"m_r\">エピソード 1</span>調査中。"
  },
  {
   "type": "timeline",
   "rows": [
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　群馬県出身。海軍機関学校卒業。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　横須賀海軍工廠内の飛行機工場長を経て大尉で退官、飛行機研究所を創立。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　のち、中島飛行機株式会社と改称、戦時下にめざましい発展を遂げる。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　事業のかたわら政界に進出、その資金力ゆえに「政友会の金袋」と言われる。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　商工政務次官を経て<a href=\"../1937/kono1_1.html\">近衛内閣①</a>の鉄相に就任。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　<a href=\"../p/hiciro.html\">鳩山一郎</a>と政友会総裁の地位を争い、分裂後、中島派政友会の総裁となる。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　内閣参議、大政翼賛会総務などを経て、<a href=\"../1945/higa_1.html\">東久邇宮内閣</a>の軍需相。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　Ａ級戦犯に指定されるも、のち釈放される。"
      }
     ]
    }
   ]
  },
